Bugfix: Default to group `snapshots --latest <n>` by host and paths

Restic 0.19.0 changed the behavior of `snapshots --latest <n>` to no longer
group snapshots by default. This default grouping has been restored. To get
this behavior with restic 0.19.0, use `snapshots --latest <n> --group-by host,paths`.

Note that snapshots are still explicitly grouped, which is different from
the restic 0.19.0 behavior that returned the snapshots in a single ungrouped
list.

https://github.com/restic/restic/issues/21869
